    "We therefore suggest a few additional responsibilities in the Appendix.",
    "Note that we only focus on responsibilities that would reduce societal risks from AI (see RQ2).",
    "Providing advice to leadershipThe ethics board could provide strategic advice to the board of directors or senior management.",
